&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duty 14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; Structure their work, prioritising appointments and managing a diverse caseload to ensure that end users receive the appropriate levels of care and support.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
