&lt;p&gt;Can the apprentice make judgements regarding the prioritisation of appointments and their caseload, in order to keep appointment schedules to time, allowing sufficient and appropriate time for different types of consultation, while delivering a focussed and professional service to the end user.&lt;/p&gt;
